Personal Notes: I didn't reach anywhere near this close to completion on my Wii playthroughs and they always took over 100 hours. Collecting for Colony 6 can still be a headache but that is the only side content that will take some time, and that's by design. Even still, every single collectible can be bought with currency from the time attack mode, so if you'd rather grind combat challenges than wandering aimlessly through late game areas that option is available from early in the game.
